{
  "stem": "10358.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for about a mile, a mile and a half, he was in the back of me, escorting me to the forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw from distance there were-- and as I was walking, marching, I was stepping-- I stepped on all the furs, jewelry, because people took their possessions.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They thought maybe they're being relocated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they made them drop everything, so when they got to this place, they were-- they didn't have any possessions with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I marched with this Nazi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I came to the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I found my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was already separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They immediately took the older men, the religious people, the sick people from hospitals, and they separated them from the women and children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was all day with my mother on a very hot day, in the hot sun, no water, no food, just standing and screaming and crying.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody else did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember distinctly black birds flying all over us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I asked my mother, what are all the black birds doing here?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, that's a bad sign.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means they're going to kill us here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Black birds usually come when there is a tragedy, when there is disaster.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were there from early in the morning until late in the evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then 'til-- we were surrounded by all the Nazis, all-- and Ukrainian police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then an order came that the women and children can go home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother and I went back to the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was no longer with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the next morning, I got up-- got up very early.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I heard that they took some people to a-- to a different area town, like the prison.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
